%% 3.2.2 View Guardian Profile — sequence
%% GET /api/Account/Me (Bearer) — same as getMe()
%% BR10: Profile data must mirror User entity (AccountDto)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Guardian as Guardian
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant AC as AccountController
    participant AS as AccountService
    participant Repo as IRepository User
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Guardian->>App: Open Profile tab
    App->>AC: GET /api/Account/Me Authorization Bearer
    AC->>AS: GetMeAsync(userId from claims)
    AS->>Repo: User + Role
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    AS-->>AC: AccountDto
    AC-->>App: 200 OK
    App->>Guardian: Avatar, name, email/phone, wallet widget (call Wallet API if needed)
